As a result, players were supposed to use their own external chat solution. But not any more...</p><p><br></p><p>We discovered <a href="https://www.around.co" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><u>Around</u></a>, a videochat tool that we can whole-heartedly recommend to use with Codenames Online. Luckily, the people from Around turned out to be big Codenames fans, so we were able to work together to create an even more integrated solution. </p><p><br></p><p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p><p><br></p><p>To give it a try simply click the "<strong>Play with videochat</strong>" button, and after starting the game in Around, invite other players in the same way you've always done it, by sending them the URL link.</p><p><br></p><p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p><p><br></p><p>You can play the game in Around both on desktop and mobile devices. At the moment, the mobile version of Around supports only a voicechat (without a video). The person who creates the videochat room must be on a desktop computer (and needs to sign in to Around), but other players can join as guests from any device.</p><p><br></p><p>So grab your friends and enjoy Codenames Online face to face.</p></section></details></article><article class="jsx-3192414555 px-4 mb-4"><details open="" class="jsx-3192414555"><summary class="jsx-3192414555 mb-2 cursor-pointer"><h2 class="jsx-3192414555 inline text-base font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer text-blue-news">Happy Holidays</h2><p class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm text-red-news">A special event for Holidays 2021.</p></summary><section class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm"><p><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/Happy Holidays.jpg"></p><p><br></p><p>How are your Holidays preparations going? Some of our agents already dressed for the occasion. So gather your loved ones and invite them to a Holidays game of Codenames Online.</p><p><br></p><p>To set the right mood, you can turn on the Holiday word pack which is now highlighted among other bonus packs in the game settings. (the Holidays pack is available in EN, CZ, DE and ES).</p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/Holidays word pack.jpg"></p><p><br></p><p>Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year from the whole Codenames Online team!</p></section></details></article><article class="jsx-3192414555 px-4 mb-4"><details open="" class="jsx-3192414555"><summary class="jsx-3192414555 mb-2 cursor-pointer"><h2 class="jsx-3192414555 inline text-base font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer text-blue-news">Galaxy Trucker Week</h2><p class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm text-red-news">A special event for November 2021, celebrating the new edition of our very first game.</p></summary><section class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm"><p><a href="https://galaxytrucker.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/Galaxy_trucker_banner.jpg"></a></p><p><br></p><p>It all begun back in 2007, eight years before the Codenames board game even came out. A small group of enthusiasts associated in a company called <a href="https://czechgames.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><u>Czech Games Edition</u></a> released their first game named <a href="https://galaxytrucker.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><u>Galaxy Trucker</u></a> - a frenetic action where you build a spaceship out of junk and test it against the perils of the universe.</p><p><br></p><p>From then on, the game got several expansions, it was released as an app and it even got its own book. And this year, we've decided to bring it back in a shiny new edition.</p><p><br></p><p>To celebrate the Galaxy Trucker Week we invited a few characters to join the fun and we added a thematic pack with the words from the Galaxy Trucker universe (available in CZ an EN), which you can find among the other bonus packs from now on.&nbsp;For an even better immersion, we recommend to play it with our dark mode feature. ;-)</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Enjoy the party and to find out more, visit </strong><a href="https://galaxytrucker.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><u>galaxytrucker.com</u></strong></a><strong>.</strong></p><p><strong>﻿</strong></p><p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt=""></p><p><br></p><p>You can always switch back to the original Codenames theme in the settings.</p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/Enable event skin.jpg"></p></section></details></article><article class="jsx-3192414555 px-4 mb-4"><details open="" class="jsx-3192414555"><summary class="jsx-3192414555 mb-2 cursor-pointer"><h2 class="jsx-3192414555 inline text-base font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer text-blue-news">Sound notification</h2><p class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm text-red-news">Let's you know when it's your turn.</p></summary><section class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm"><p>Have you missed the clue? Turn on the sound notification to know right away.&nbsp;</p><p></p><p>You can find it under the button with your nickname in the top right corner, together with other personal settings.</p><p><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/Sound notification.jpg"></p></section></details></article><article class="jsx-3192414555 px-4 mb-4"><details open="" class="jsx-3192414555"><summary class="jsx-3192414555 mb-2 cursor-pointer"><h2 class="jsx-3192414555 inline text-base font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer text-blue-news">Dark Mode</h2><p class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm text-red-news">Enjoy the new fresh look.</p></summary><section class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm"><p>Whether the current screen might be too bright for your eyes or you simply want to try something different, we have a new dark mode for you.</p><p><br></p><p>You can find it under the button with your nickname in the top right corner.</p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/DarkMode.jpg"></p></section></details></article><article class="jsx-3192414555 px-4 mb-4"><details open="" class="jsx-3192414555"><summary class="jsx-3192414555 mb-2 cursor-pointer"><h2 class="jsx-3192414555 inline text-base font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer text-blue-news">Timer</h2><p class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm text-red-news">Add some preasure with one of the three timer modes.</p></summary><section class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm"><p>The game's host can setup the timer by clicking the button in the top left corner:</p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://cno-admin-upload.eu-central-1.linodeobjects.com/timer.jpg"></p><p><br></p><p>You can play as you've been used to, without a timer. But if you decide to use it, you can choose among the three possible modes:</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Manual </strong>- Simply click the timer when someone thinks for too long.</p><p><strong>Automatic for side</strong> - The time is shared by the whole team, and it is up to them how much of it they use for clues and how much for guessing.</p><p><strong>Automatic for ro</strong>le - It allows you to set a different time for&nbsp;operatives and for spymasters.</p><p><br></p><p>If the time runs out, the game does not switch to the other team automatically. It is up to you how to solve the situation, just like when playing on a table.</p></section></details></article><article class="jsx-3192414555 px-4 mb-4"><details open="" class="jsx-3192414555"><summary class="jsx-3192414555 mb-2 cursor-pointer"><h2 class="jsx-3192414555 inline text-base font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer text-blue-news">Custom Pack</h2><p class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm text-red-news">Add your own words with the custom pack feature.</p></summary><section class="jsx-3192414555 text-sm"><p>The <strong>custom word pack</strong> can be found among the other word packs.</p><p>Simply fill in your words or write them down in a txt file (one word per line) and drag it in the box.
